title: Vineyard Vines font?!
content:
I'm looking for the vineyard vines clothing font. Anyone know what it's called or where I could get it for free??  
Thanks!

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150215061130im_/http:/typophile.com/files/logo_vv-main_4255.gif)

comments.content:
It looks like [Mrs Eaves](http://web.archive.org/web/20150215061130/http:/www.emigre.com/EF.php?fid=109) and it's not free. Some graphics programs come with Baskerville, which is similar.
